/* Welcome / About */
"I live in the menu bar and keep your Mac awake while Codex or Claude Code are working — then let it sleep when they stop.\n\nThere's nothing to set up. Look for the bolt in the menu bar." = "我住在選單列裡，會在 Codex 或 Claude Code 執行時讓你的 Mac 保持喚醒，工作結束後再讓它睡眠。\n\n無需任何設定。在選單列中找閃電圖示即可。";
"Get Started" = "開始使用";
"Version %@\n\nKeeps your Mac awake while Codex or Claude Code are working.\n\nLid-closed mode adds one narrow sudoers rule for the exact pmset commands it needs, and backs off automatically if your Mac gets too warm. Remove it anytime from Advanced." = "版本 %@\n\n在 Codex 或 Claude Code 執行時讓你的 Mac 保持喚醒。\n\n合蓋模式只會為其所需的特定 pmset 指令新增一條範圍很窄的 sudoers 規則，並在 Mac 過熱時自動停止。你可以隨時在「進階」中移除它。";
"OK" = "好";

